title: Julia Davis - Top Priority - The Terror Within
description: This is not original issue. Just retransmitted.  This is the story of US DHS agent who was accused of being "domestic terrorist" !  Another story of the decline of democracy and freedom into government's vision of the police state. This story needs to be seen and shared with others.  Be vigilant my brothers and sisters !  Wake up and stand up !  Do good and be good !   Spread peace and not hate !
